title: Quick BBQ Chicken Sandwiches with Smoked Paprika Mayo & Lime Slaw
description: Evoke your favorite summertime memories—the smell of barbecue wafting through the warm evening air, crickets chirping, the sound of kids playing outdoors—with this delicious sandwich that’s ready in just 10 minutes. Slather juicy, fully cooked chicken with rich BBQ sauce and tuck into a soft brioche bun spread with smoky paprika mayo. Top with tangy cabbage slaw and fresh tomatoes for color and crunch, and enjoy the cookout vibe!
